                "title": "冰锥迸射"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">四迸冰锥</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/0124980d7537e933e9e0e819b78a0733_7069975472410772511.png",
                "id": "talent16120",
                "key": "圆舞冰环",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "圆舞冰环"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素伤害</span>，对所有敌方后台角色造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">刺击冰棱</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/77df8fb6101bdb6c35d501967b98f941_340543724233840783.png",
                "id": "talent68821",
                "key": "冰棱轰坠",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰棱轰坠"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，初始附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">冰晶核心</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/c9fb58d0c17579d0eca97a167035bc53_5680065076148795581.png",
                "id": "talent13429",
                "key": "冰晶核心",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰晶核心"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>对敌方<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">距离我方出战角色</span>最近的角色造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7505556502813908036.png",
                "id": "talent68246",
                "key": "刺击冰棱",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/9a3a650b50940ebaf9e842bccc80f213_1156127714690549596.png",
                "title": "刺击冰棱"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">融化</span>：本伤害<span>+2</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">超导</span>：本伤害<span>+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害<span>+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_5540975596832916220.png",
                "id": "talent73719",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">距离我方出战角色最近的角色<br></span></strong>对方场上距离我方出战角色「最近」的角色，指的是位置与我方出战角色最接近的敌方角色。<br>如果存在多个位置最接近的角色，则其中靠前的角色被视为「最近」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免于被击倒<br></span></strong>一些效果会使角色在生命值被降为0的时候<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免于被击倒</span>，并治疗该角色到一定生命值。<br>此时，角色不视为被<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">击倒</span>过。（因此，角色所附属的装备和状态不会被弃置，充能也不会被清空。）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">四迸冰锥</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色进行普通攻击时：</span>对所有敌方后台角色造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冰晶核心</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色被击倒时：</span>移除此效果，使角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免于被击倒</span>，并治疗该角色到1点生命值。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_2505798791123799939.png",
